desc:
Use: Eat Tree or Ward - Consume a tree or ward to restore health over time. Eating a ward provides double healing. Eat cast range is increased when targetting wards. Comes with 4 charges.

Use on an allied hero to give them one Tango.
attrib:
EAT TREE HEALTH RESTORED: 115
EAT WARD HEALTH RESTORED: 230
EAT WARD CAST RANGE: 450
HEAL DURATION: 16
lore: Forage to survive on the battlefield.
